        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2691",
        "content": "In attempting to cross the distance from her camp to his, she had strayed and wandered about far into the night, and finally reached his cabin wet, shivering, and grief stricken, yet determined to push onward.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
