        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2691/156750/2691_156750_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2691",
        "content": "Grandpa brought the news home, \"California is ours.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2691_156750_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2691/156750/2691_156750_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2691",
        "content": "Yet the women felt that their battles and trials had just begun, since they had suddenly become the sole home keepers, with limited ways and means to provide for the children and care for the stock and farms. Discouragement would have rendered the burdens of many too heavy to carry, had not \"work together,\" and \"help your neighbor,\" become the watchwords of the day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2691_156750_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2691/156750/2691_156750_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2691",
        "content": "No one was allowed to suffer through lack of practical sympathy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2691_156750_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2691/156750/2691_156750_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2691",
        "content": "Nights, she set her shoes handy, so that she could dress quickly when summoned to the sick; and dawn of day often marked her home coming.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2691_156750_000014_000001",
